  "description": "<p>Job Summary</p><p>We're looking for a Solution Sales Consultant to drive growth through our partner network, selling physical security Integration solutions (CCTV, access control, etc.).- Drive sales growth for physical security technology solutions</p><p>- Identify and pursue new business opportunities in the security tech space</p><p>- Collaborate with product and marketing teams to align sales efforts</p><p>- Provide product demos for security solutions</p><p>- Build strong relationships with clients and partners in the security industry</p><p>- Consultative Selling: Acting as a trusted advisor to understand customer pain points and providing tailored solutions</p><p></p><p>Skills:</p><p>- Experience in security tech sales or related field</p><p>- Strong communication and presentation skills</p><p>- Strategic thinking</p><p>- Relationship building</p><p>- Technical knowledge of physical security solutions</p>",
